<knimeNode icon="./default.png" type="Manipulator">
    <name>Anonymisation</name>
    
    <shortDescription>
        Encrypts and decrypts selected input data using symmetric algorithm (DES), using provided encryption key.
    </shortDescription>
    
    <fullDescription>
        <intro> It can translate one set of data to another with the same structure 
        as origin and encrypt important information. To provide security, symmetrical translation (encryption and decryption) 
        and constant output for the same input data uses key base encryption algorithm (Blowfish)</intro>
        
        
        <option name="Anonymization">Chose columns for anonymization</option>
        <option name="De-anonymization">Chose columns for de-anonymization</option>
